<p>We have a healthy mix of Linux, Windows and Mac and for me the major problem usually comes down to managing authentication and permissions. We have an AD domain which I use for authentication and I got it linked through to Linux without too many issues but generally I get problems with permissions via Services for NFS/Samba. </p>
